OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778609470
OL,3,CDoctors across Northern Ireland to be
OL,4,Cballoted for industrial action
OL,6,FThe first collective ballot of all
OL,7,Fsecondary care doctors working in
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland on taking strike
OL,9,Faction over pay opened on Monday.
OL,11,FConsultants, specialist doctors and
OL,12,Fresident doctors are all being asked
OL,13,Ftake part in the pay.
OL,15,FIt comes as doctors have rejected a
OL,16,Fproposed 3.5 percent pay uplift,
OL,17,Fsaying it does not address years of
OL,18,Fpay erosion or reflect the highly
OL,19,Fpressurised work doctors are
OL,20,Fresponsible for.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
