OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778609470
OL,3,CDoctors across Northern Ireland to be
OL,4,Cballoted for industrial action
OL,6,FDr David Farren from the BMA says
OL,7,Fmorale among doctors has been
OL,8,Fseriously damaged.
OL,10,FHe said: "This is a completely
OL,11,Funprecedented situation that we are
OL,12,Fin. The public will remember that
OL,13,Fwe've had strikes for the resident
OL,14,Fdoctors, in previous years and
OL,15,Fconsultants balloted for strike
OL,16,Faction, but were able to avoid that
OL,17,Fwith negotiation two years ago.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778609470
OL,3,CDoctors across Northern Ireland to be
OL,4,Cballoted for industrial action
OL,6,F"But we have never seen all grades of
OL,7,Fhospital doctors taking a ballot for
OL,8,Findustrial action at the same time,
OL,9,Fand that's because of the consistent
OL,10,Ffailure to deliver on a policy of full
OL,11,Fpay restoration for doctors.
OL,13,F"I've been working as a doctor in
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland since 2002, and my
OL,15,Fsalary has decreased in real terms
OL,16,Fover the last fifteen years by about
OL,17,F20 to 25 percent depending on what
OL,18,Fmeasure of inflation you use.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778609470
OL,3,CDoctors across Northern Ireland to be
OL,4,Cballoted for industrial action
OL,6,F"I'm not 20 percent less good as a
OL,7,Fdoctor than I was 15 years ago, I'm
OL,8,Fnot doing 20 percent less work, but
OL,9,FI'm being paid 20 percent less."
OL,11,FThe Department of Health says it is
OL,12,Fdisappointed by the decision to ballot
OL,13,Ffor industrial action, but says the
OL,14,FHealth Minister remains committed to
OL,15,Fimplementing this year's 3.5 percent
OL,16,Fpay award once budgets are agreed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,446,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F445A1778609470
OL,3,CDoctors across Northern Ireland to be
OL,4,Cballoted for industrial action
OL,6,FIt says the offer is higher than that
OL,7,Frecommended for other healthcare
OL,8,Fworkers and insists there is no scope
OL,9,Fto go beyond it because of financial
OL,10,Fpressures.
OL,12,FThe BMA says strike action again is
OL,13,Fnot something doctors want to do ` but
OL,14,Fwarns if pay erosion is not addressed,
OL,15,Fmore doctors will leave the profession.
OL,17,FThe ballot will remain open until the
OL,18,F8th of June.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/6
